high_descs: Go forward and face the sink on your left.
Take the spray bottle from the sink in front of you.
Turn left then face the can on your right.
Place the spray bottle in the can in front of you.
Turn right and face the sink on your left.
Take the spray bottle from the counter in front of you.
Turn left then face the can on your right.
Place the spray bottle in the can in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place the spray bottle in the can.

high_descs: Go forward, turn left at the sink, go forward to the left side of the sink.
Take the white spray bottle from the sink counter.
Go to the left in front of the towel.
Put the spray bottle in the trash bin below the towel.
Turn right, go to the right side of the sink.
Take the white spray bottle from the sink counter.
Turn left, go back in front of the towel.
Put the spray bottle in the trash bin below the towel.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles in a trash bin.

high_descs: Go forward to the front of the sink on the left.
Pick up the white spray bottle on the left sink counter.
Move over left to the gray trash can on the floor.
Place the white spray bottle in the trash can.
Turn right and go to the front right side of the sink on the left.
Pick up the white spray bottle on the right sink counter.
Turn left and go back to the trash gray can on the floor on the left of the sink.
Place the white spray bottle in the trash can to the right of the first spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Throw out two spray bottles on the sink.
